Tam Minh is a diversified yet specialised solution providers. We offer full package services from design, technical supports, delivery, site implementation and installation of highly differentiated solutions for building projects and homes.

We have three pillars in our business: 

(i) Specialised science laboratory furniture systems and sustainable drinking solutions;
(ii) Lighting;
(iii) Home Elevators.

